<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inter:400,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e3e7ed 100%);
      color: #222;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 56px 40px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .container::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px;
      left: -60px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, #6366f1 0%, #3b82f6 80%, transparent 100%);
      opacity: 0.18;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .container::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -60px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 80%, transparent 100%);
      opacity: 0.12;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 72px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: #3b82f6;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(59,130,246,0.10);
      transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(59,130,246,0.18);
      transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }
    .feature {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #333;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(59,130,246,0.04);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #6366f1;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 28px 8px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 48px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/Stripe_Logo%2C_revised_2016.svg/320px-Stripe_Logo%2C_revised_2016.svg.png" alt="Stripe Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Stripe Checkout Pages</h1>
    <p>Build beautiful, secure payment experiences with Node.js, Express, and EJS.<br>Start with a modern MVC template and customize for your brand.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Get Started</a>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon">üí≥</span> Seamless Stripe Integration</div>
      <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon">‚ö°</span> Fast & Responsive UI</div>
      <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon">üîí</span> Secure Payment Flows</div>
      <div class="feature"><span class="feature-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</span> Easy Customization</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
